Musm trnovat sama... :(

243
00:12:20,266 --> 00:12:22,017
Musm si od nkoho pjit m...

244
00:12:22,551 --> 00:12:23,203
Musm trnovat sama...

245
00:12:23,203 --> 00:12:25,121
Co si to muml?
Musm trnovat sama...

246
00:12:25,121 --> 00:12:26,022
Leze mi z toho mrz po zdech...
Musm si pjit m...

247
00:12:26,022 --> 00:12:27,540
Se Sadako nco je!
Musm si pjit m...

248
00:12:27,540 --> 00:12:28,599
Se Sadako nco je!
Musm trnovat sama...

249
00:12:28,599 --> 00:12:29,575
To, elem vzad.
Musm trnovat sama...

250
00:12:30,851 --> 00:12:33,137
