251
00:12:35,506 --> 00:12:36,515
Jsem volnej!

252
00:12:36,966 --> 00:12:38,767
To je Kazehaya-kun!

253
00:12:40,085 --> 00:12:41,345
Co to proboha pedvd?

254
00:12:41,345 --> 00:12:43,731
Tohle by zvldli i prvci...

255
00:12:45,449 --> 00:12:46,634
Vypad to, e se bav!

256
00:12:47,159 --> 00:12:49,236
Byla jsem schopn ho vidt sportovat...

257
00:12:49,520 --> 00:12:52,573
Zajmalo by m, jestli rd hraje softball.

258
00:12:53,282 --> 00:12:57,703
U konete, kluci! Za chvli zvon!

259
00:12:58,061 --> 00:12:58,904
Jop, dky!

260
00:13:00,422 --> 00:13:02,416
Tak konme!

261
00:13:08,247 --> 00:13:09,140
M hezk es.

262
00:13:11,943 --> 00:13:14,119
Kazehayo, pohni!

263
00:13:14,119 --> 00:13:14,812
U jdu!

264
00:13:31,837 --> 00:13:32,997
Sadako?

265
00:13:43,991 --> 00:13:45,284
Kuronuma Sawako!!!

266
00:13:47,411 --> 00:13:49,188
Na co to civ?

267
00:13:49,188 --> 00:13:50,598
U musme jt!

268
00:13:50,598 --> 00:13:52,199
Jsi njak rud...

269
00:13:52,199 --> 00:13:53,942
Coe? Fakt?

270
00:13:53,942 --> 00:13:56,103
To jsi tak vyzen?

271
00:13:56,103 --> 00:13:58,922
N-ne... Tm to nen...

272
00:13:58,922 --> 00:14:01,550
Wtf? Co se to se mnou dje?

273
00:14:01,550 --> 00:14:04,904
On pece neekl nic nenormlnho!

274
00:14:05,638 --> 00:14:07,456
Byli jsme od sebe taky pkn daleko!

275
00:14:07,456 --> 00:14:10,384
Prost jenom el pry...

276
00:14:17,833 --> 00:14:21,321
J-j-j... P-prost nemu....

277
00:14:22,505 --> 00:14:24,381
P-prost z nho nemu spustit oi...

278
00:14:28,411 --> 00:14:29,420
Postavit!

279
00:14:30,813 --> 00:14:31,597
Sednout.

280
00:14:32,256 --> 00:14:33,800
Konen! Zvonek zvon, kola kon!

281
00:14:33,800 --> 00:14:35,810
Pojme se nadlbnout, Yano-chin!

282
00:14:35,810 --> 00:14:39,146
Sadako, nem chu na ramen?

283
00:14:39,146 --> 00:14:40,264
Ne!

284
00:14:40,264 --> 00:14:42,141
Pesta s tm, nebo budu tlust!

285
00:14:43,609 --> 00:14:46,520
Nechtla's nhodou nco koupit?

286
00:14:46,520 --> 00:14:50,232
No jo! Potebuju si koupit erven triko, abych na
festivale nevypadala jako ostatn!

287
00:14:50,825 --> 00:14:52,259
Pjde s nmi, Sadako?

288
00:14:52,259 --> 00:14:57,590
M-mm jet njakou prci... 
Musm zalt kytiky a tak...

289
00:14:57,590 --> 00:14:59,058
Mon nkdy pt...

290
00:14:59,058 --> 00:15:00,342
Fakt?

291
00:15:00,709 --> 00:15:03,820
V, e bychom na tebe pokaly...

292
00:15:03,820 --> 00:15:05,789
A kdy ti pomeme, tak to bude rychleji hotov...

293
00:15:05,789 --> 00:15:08,625
N-ne, dky, zvldnu to sama...

294
00:15:09,135 --> 00:15:11,670
Ale..  Byla bych rda...

295
00:15:13,889 --> 00:15:16,434
Kdybych s vmi mohla jt pt.

296
00:15:17,184 --> 00:15:18,702
Samo. Klidn s nma potej...

297
00:15:18,702 --> 00:15:20,688
Take pt pjde s nmi, ok?

298
00:15:21,130 --> 00:15:22,039
Tak jo!

299
00:15:22,548 --> 00:15:28,279
Jsou na m moc mil. Kdy jim eknu e se um,
trvaj na tom, e mi pomou.

300
00:15:28,629 --> 00:15:29,697
Dokonce ikdy u maj nco v plnu.

301
00:15:30,739 --> 00:15:33,942
Zeptm se vs, kdy mte volno...

302
00:15:33,942 --> 00:15:35,344
Hrozn si vs dvou cenm...

303
00:15:36,187 --> 00:15:38,747
Co m v plnu te, Kazehayo?

304
00:15:40,082 --> 00:15:41,542
Hmm, musm jt na tu schzku komise...
To je Kazehaya-kun!

305
00:15:41,542 --> 00:15:42,593
Neekejte na m...

306
00:15:42,593 --> 00:15:44,395
Ach jo, ta pitom komise...

307
00:15:44,395 --> 00:15:46,839
No jo, a pitomej Pin...

308
00:15:46,839 --> 00:15:47,615
Pesn!

309
00:15:49,241 --> 00:15:52,303
Co to vlastn dlm?

310
00:16:14,308 --> 00:16:17,711
Coe, ty si chce pjit m?

311
00:16:17,711 --> 00:16:20,389
Ano. Byla bych vm hrozn vdn...

312
00:16:20,389 --> 00:16:21,874
Ne... ne...

313
00:16:21,874 --> 00:16:24,284
Promi, ale nemu lidem pjovat me...

314
00:16:24,284 --> 00:16:26,278
Pro ne?

315
00:16:26,278 --> 00:16:28,088
Psahm, e vm ho vrtm zptky!

316
00:16:28,088 --> 00:16:29,732
Ne znamen ne!

317
00:16:35,454 --> 00:16:37,598
Stejn to byla jenom prkotina...

318
00:16:38,307 --> 00:16:41,377
Myslm, e si asi koupm vlastn m...

319
00:16:41,836 --> 00:16:43,829
...z toho, co dostanu jako kapesn...

320
00:16:46,741 --> 00:16:49,059
Jsou ta okna ist?

321
00:16:49,059 --> 00:16:50,436
Jop.

322
00:16:53,981 --> 00:16:58,786
Tady to bylo poprv,
 co jsem si s Kazehayou-kunem podn popovdala.

323
00:17:26,839 --> 00:17:27,548
Huh?

324
00:17:27,548 --> 00:17:29,925
Ty jsi v komisi, e?

325
00:17:29,925 --> 00:17:30,668
Mmh.

326
00:17:31,594 --> 00:17:32,695
Ty jsi taky byla nominovan, co?

327
00:17:32,695 --> 00:17:33,612
Jsem rd, e jsem nebyl jedin...

328
00:17:34,713 --> 00:17:36,882
Myslm, e jsme oba mli smlu...

329
00:17:36,882 --> 00:17:38,617
Mimochodem, to msto pede mnou je voln...

330
00:17:38,617 --> 00:17:40,302
Oh, dky.

331
00:17:42,788 --> 00:17:44,415
