341
00:18:37,105 --> 00:18:38,503
Kampak to jde?

342
00:19:03,928 --> 00:19:04,595
Huups?

343
00:19:04,895 --> 00:19:07,665
To u zvon?

344
00:19:47,485 --> 00:19:48,114
Poj...

345
00:20:01,586 --> 00:20:02,928
Nevm pro...

346
00:20:04,647 --> 00:20:07,958
