347
00:20:19,754 --> 00:20:22,740
Vzduch byl... pjemnj... ne obvykle...

348
00:20:36,621 --> 00:20:39,965
Take namsto smvu...

349
00:20:51,511 --> 00:20:53,379
...se radi budu snait...

350
00:21:14,626 --> 00:21:25,204
Chci se stt vlatovkou a vznet se k nebesm...

351
